    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in total showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, this is the one! Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
