    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a rigid chassis with zero subframe fatigue and a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque vectoring. All critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory finish remains in showroom condition, preserving the aerodynamic integrity and aesthetic of this naturally aspirated icon. A turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak BMW M performance.",
